Predators of the Deep is a suspense thriller that delves into the treacherous journey of Miguel and his group of friends as they embark on a perilous mission to uncover the hidden treasures of the sunken Santa Ynez shipwreck. Set against the menacing backdrop of the Atlantic coast, their once-exciting expedition quickly morphs into a nightmarish fight for survival as they find themselves hopelessly lost in the vast, unforgiving ocean.
